\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The University of KwaZulu-Natal is a public institution offering in a contact mode. The institution has also made application for the accreditation of a Bachelor of Arts \'28Honours\'29 and a Doctor of Philosophy in International Relations.\line \line The Accreditation Committee decided at its meeting of 01 June 2011 to defer this programme pending the appointment of a second evaluator. \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
